   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>To my good friend and fellow,
THOMAS HEYVVOOD.</head>
   <l>HAue I not knowne a man that to be hyr'd,</l>
   <l>Would not for any treasure see a play,</l>
   <l>Reele from a Tauerne? Shall this be admir'd?</l>
   <l>When as another but the tother day,</l>
   <l>That held to weare a surplesse most vnmeet,</l>
   <l>Yet after stood at <hi>Pauls-crosse</hi> in a sheet.</l>
   <signed>Robert Pallant.</signed>
</div>
